		<div id="comment_body_64264888"><p><div class="quote"><blockquote><div><p>working-from-home...reduces pollution</p></div></blockquote><p>Could you post a link to that study?</p></div><p>It's kinda obvious, but if you really need a link, here's one I found with a five-second Google search:</p><p><span class="substr"> </span> <a href="https://news.cornell.edu/stories/2023/09/lifestyle-impacts-green-benefits-remote-work" title="cornell.edu">Green benefits of remote work</a> [cornell.edu] </p><p>From the link: <i>"Remote workers can have a 54% lower carbon footprint compared with onsite workers, according to a new study by Cornell and Microsoft"</i> </p></div>
	</div>

